===================
Pinax Announcements
===================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pinax-announcements.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pinax-announcements/
.. image:: https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pinax-announcements/

